gametitle=Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas (NTSC-U SLUS-20946 / CRC 399A49CA)
comment=Vehicle-only PS2 Controller Remapper hook attempt.
comment=Based on PS2 Controller Remapper output plus vehicle gate using 0x0066BB48.
comment=Target: original NTSC-U SLUS-209.46, CRC 399A49CA.

[Cheats\Vehicle-only R2-L2 driving remap]
description=On foot: stock controls. In vehicle: R2/RT -> Cross gas, L2/LT -> Square brake/reverse.
author=Zeroable + PS2 Controller Remapper by pelvicthrustman + ChatGPT assembly/debugging

